g.text: Consumer usage of online legal services has more than doubled, from 21% in 2012 to 44% in 2021.As expected, the pandemic accelerated this shift to online delivery, with 54% of consumers using online services during the pandemic.

30% of consumers shopped around for a legal services provider in 2021, compared to 22% in 2012.Legal Utopia allows consumers to discover your firm through our Find A Lawyer service, giving your firm a much greater reach.
